Quote: Rowe scooped up the animal in his arms, careful to keep its damaged hip away from his body. At the connex, he laid the child on the hot, stinking metal. Rowe stepped outside and began to close the doors. He stopped, staring at the mangled creatures inside, his face hung low. He swung the doors shut and vomited in the dust. Did he say… child? Kim wasn’t sure. She pushed past it. I’m sorry you had to do that, Kim said. Why didn’t you report it to someone?
